messages.content: Hey all! Welcome to the official Infinite Flight Discord server (cue clapping and cheering)! I've noticed a lot of the new folks joining haven't linked their Infinite Flight accounts to Discord. You can do this in account settings in the app. Once this is done, it may take some time to sync to Discord. If it still hasn't synced after 24 hours **and your account is linked** please contact support via the forum. Cheers!

Folks, if you're trying to join the Pro-only sections and have *already* linked your account, please try one of the following:

 - Leave this server and rejoin using this link (copy it before leaving): discord.gg/infiniteflight
 - Unlink your Discord account in the Infinite Flight app, and relink it and wait a bit longer.

If _both_ of these fail, please contact support via the forum. Thanks!

What would you like to see for our next Pilot Lounge event? React 👇🏼 

1️⃣: More real world aviation talk
2️⃣: Developer talk
3️⃣: Mod talk
4️⃣: IFATC talk
5️⃣: Other? (Will thread in #deleted-channel)

Our first Discord poll exclusively for Pro subscribers has come to an end! We asked you to choose the next 3D ATC Tower that would be added to our development pipeline. 

With 364 votes, the winner is **Hong Kong (VHHH)**! 

**POLL RESULTS**
🥇 Hong Kong (VHHH) - 364 [54%]
🥈 Singapore (WSSS) - 250 [37%]
🥉 Tokyo Haneda (RJTT) - 59 [9%]

There is no timeline for development and it may not be the next custom tower introduced, however the winner of this poll has been guaranteed for creation and implementation in Infinite Flight. Thank you for being an Infinite Flight Pro subscriber! :infiniteflight:

_PC 📸 : jetphotos.net_

Our 2nd exclusive poll for Pro Subscribers to determine the next custom ATC Tower has concluded. The winner has been committed to future development. With an impressive 791 votes making up 66% of all votes cast, the winner is....

:controltower: **Frankfurt (EDDF)** :controltower: 

🏅 **POLL RESULTS** 🏅 
1. Frankfurt (EDDF) - 791 votes / 66%
2. Rome (LIRF) - 148 votes / 12%
3. Manchester (EGCC) - 99 votes / 8%
4. Geneva (LSGG) - 88 votes / 7%
5. Vienna (LOWW) - 72 votes / 6%

There is no timeline for development and it may not be the next custom tower introduced, however the winner of this poll has been guaranteed for creation and implementation in Infinite Flight. Thank you for being an Infinite Flight Pro subscriber! :infiniteflight:
